INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (281,1,'2013-05-23 18:46:52','2013-05-23 22:46:52','<p class=\"p1\">We understand being without your Mac can be tough, so we strive to complete certain repairs and upgrades within an hour whenever possible. If we are replacing a functioning hard drive with a larger one and transferring the data (or installing a new drive with no data transfer), we can often do it in 24 hours (on weekdays). Otherwise, the standard turnaround time for most repairs is three business days. We offer flat-rate computer rentals during a Tekserve repair. For a list of available machines and pricing, please visit <a href=\"http://www.tekserve.com/rentals\">tekserve.com/rentals</a>.</p>','How long will the repair take?','','publish','open','open','','how-long-will-the-repair-take','','','2013-06-18 17:11:21','2013-06-18 21:11:21','',0,'http://localhost/tekfaqs/?p=281',35,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (282,1,'2013-05-23 18:46:48','2013-05-23 22:46:48','<p class=\"p1\">We understand being without your Mac can be tough, so we strive to complete certain repairs and upgrades within an hour whenever possible. If we are replacing a functioning hard drive with a larger one and transferring the data (or installing a new drive with no data transfer), we can often do it in 24 hours (on weekdays). Otherwise, the standard turnaround time for most repairs is three business days. We offer flat-rate computer rentals during a Tekserve repair. For a list of available machines and pricing, please visit <a href=\"http://www.tekserve.com/rentals\">tekserve.com/rentals</a>.</p>','How long will the repair take?','','inherit','open','open','','281-revision','','','2013-05-23 18:46:48','2013-05-23 22:46:48','',281,'http://localhost/tekfaqs/?p=282',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (284,1,'2013-05-23 18:48:20','2013-05-23 22:48:20','<p class=\"p1\">Many failures and repairs don&rsquo;t affect the hard drive or the data, although you will not be able to access your data until the repair is done. If you were unable to back up the Mac yourself and need the data while we are fixing the computer (or just feel better having a backup), we can help. One of the services we offer is to remove the hard drive from a broken computer and back up the data, usually to an external hard drive.</p>','What if I can\'t back up my data (files)?','','publish','open','open','','what-if-i-cant-back-up-my-data-files','','','2013-06-18 17:11:21','2013-06-18 21:11:21','',0,'http://localhost/tekfaqs/?p=284',36,'post','',0);
