INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (297,1,'2013-05-23 18:58:34','2013-05-23 22:58:34','<p class=\"p1\">On a portable computer, immediately do the following things:</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">&bull; Shut down the computer and unplug the power cord.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">&bull; Remove the computer&rsquo;s battery (if you can).</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">&bull; Disconnect any peripherals (printers, iPods, scanners, cameras, etc.).</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">&bull; Lay the computer upside down on paper towels to get as much liquid as possible to drip out.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">&bull; Note what was spilled on your computer.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">&bull; Bring the Mac into Tekserve as soon as possible.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Do not try to turn it back on. Liquids can help electrical current move about the components of your Mac in destructive ways. Don&rsquo;t shake the computer (this will only spread the liquid around). Finally, don&rsquo;t use a hair dryer on it (even at a low setting a hair dryer will damage sensitive components). Liquid and spill damage is not covered by warranty or AppleCare (but may be covered by accidental damage insurance, home owners/renter insurance policies, and some credit cards). You can learn more about Tekserve&rsquo;s spill cleaning service at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.tekserve.com/faq/spill\">tekserve.com/faq/spill</a>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">If you&rsquo;ve spilled on a desktop computer&rsquo;s keyboard, shut down the computer, unplug the keyboard, and turn it upside down. Wait a day or two for it to dry. It may be okay at that point. If not, buy a new keyboard. (Former <em>BYTE</em> columnist Jerry Pournelle says to take it in the shower with you and rinse it thoroughly and then dry it for a few days - but he also believes in <em>Star Wars</em> missile defenses.) New Apple USB keyboards start at around $49 and other brands are available at Tekserve for less.</p>','I just spilled beer/tea/cough syrup on my keyboard (well, my cat threw up on it).','','publish','open','open','','i-just-spilled-beerteacough-syrup-on-my-keyboard-well-my-cat-threw-up-on-it','','','2013-06-18 17:11:42','2013-06-18 21:11:42','',0,'http://localhost/tekfaqs/?p=297',42,'post','',0);
